{"tid":1730128,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"恐怖分子：連接理大與紅磡站行人天橋被焚毀","createTime":"2019-11-17T12:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T12:37:49.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c4edb067d93f71edda828bd291c2cc89639b28c9","tid":1730128,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"警方表示，在晚上近7時，聚集在理工大學的暴徒焚毀連接理工大學與港鐵紅磡站的行人天橋，現場火勢猛烈、煙霧瀰漫，多次傳出爆炸聲，有火種由高處掉下，令火勢蔓延到橋下，嚴重危害在場所有人的人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n警方亦指，在暢運道行車天橋上，暴徒多次向警方投擲汽油彈，阻止警方推進。警方施放催淚彈驅散，雙方仍對峙中。<br />\n<br />\n警方再次呼籲市民遠離理工大學一帶，重申任何人進入或逗留在理工大學範圍，並協助暴徒，都有可能視為參與暴動。"},{"pid":"293e495ba64423ee5205bd3db31519ec1a1cd7ff","tid":1730128,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:35:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1212782&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1212782%26csid%3D261_341&d=sw6tlk2lcpT%2BYldK84vytM22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=c1fbf97e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1212782&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b2715f3b0abce32a83bf551291e005bfc695e40f","tid":1730128,"uid":237209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:37:49.000Z","msg":"炸斷未"}]}